About This Company
Experience The Ritz-Carlton, Dubai luxury hotel and discover a private playground in the heart of the vibrant Dubai Marina District. With all the opulently decorated rooms enjoying garden and ocean views, this intimately splendid resort, situated on 350 meters of the pristine white sands of the Arabian Gulf, is the perfect place to relax and indulge. Guests can bask in the sun and enjoy the warm ocean waters or the refreshing pools and waterfalls within the extensive gardens of our five-star hotel. Alternatively, you can fully relax in our stunning property with a soothing spa treatment or an exceptional meal in a breathtaking setting.
For our young guests, the superb Ritz-Kidz club, situated in close proximity to the sun-shaded children's pool and play areas, allows parents the opportunity to relax, knowing that their children's active bodies and minds will be entertained. Dubai is an increasingly dynamic destination and there are a multitude of experiences for our guests to enjoy, from exceptional shopping to perfect championship golf courses, or historic Souks to a Desert Safari, all of which are all only moments from our luxury hotel in Dubai.
